357
00:17:29,365 --> 00:17:30,365
Isn't that right?

358
00:17:30,366 --> 00:17:32,133
Yep. That's the bitch.

359
00:17:32,134 --> 00:17:34,302
Yes! Yes! I'm the bitch!

360
00:17:34,303 --> 00:17:37,939
