367
00:17:52,388 --> 00:17:54,122
Put him down. He's cool.

368
00:17:54,123 --> 00:17:57,925
Even with those clothes
and that head.

369
00:17:57,926 --> 00:18:00,895
I mean, really. Are we
that desperate for success?

370
00:18:00,896 --> 00:18:03,364
