404
00:19:27,305 --> 00:19:30,774
I remembered that was
your original cupcake shop goal.

405
00:19:30,775 --> 00:19:34,578
So when you hit that amount,
we can talk rent.

406
00:19:34,579 --> 00:19:37,581
